This is Linux(Ubuntu) version with Vim 7.3 configuration. It is a derivative of Derek Waytt's work, but lot of other customization is also there.

Steps:

1> git clone git://github.com/arindam89/vimconfigwin.git
2> Rename vimconfiglin to vim
3> Place it under Program ~
4> cd ~; mv ~/vin/vimrc .vimrc
5> mv vim .vim

